on conflict (id) do nothing;

on conflict (id) do nothing;

on conflict (id) do nothing;

on conflict (id) do nothing;

on conflict (booth_id) do nothing;

on conflict (booth_id) do nothing;

on conflict (id) do nothing;

on conflict (id) do nothing;

